idden\", \"RichText\" and \"URL\"**, but it is not needed in these TVs.\r\n\r\n2) The input field description-label is **always shown**, even if the field itself is hidden, which is strange, see the picture below.\r\n\r\n![tv_input_options_bug](https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/12523676/53235714-f0df8a00-36ab-11e9-8397-035b91c54d6e.png)\r\n\r\n### Expected behavior\r\nThe field should be displayed and **be required** only for fields for which Option Values are needed, for example, the checkbox TV.\r\nAnd the Option Values field should be checked at the stage of saving, as suggested by @JoshuaLuckers - https://github.com/modxcms/revolution/pull/14275#issuecomment-454428234 (which is a more logical option than I suggested in PR)\r\n\r\nFor the rest of the TV, this field and its description should be removed.\r\n\r\n### Environment\r\nMODX 2.7.1","performed_via_github_app":null,"score":1.0},{"url":"https://api.github.com/repos/modxcms/revolution/issues/15089","repository_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/modxcms/revolution","labels_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/modxcms/revolution/issues/15089/labels{/name}","comments_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/modxcms/revolution/issues/15089/comments","events_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/modxcms/revolution/issues/15089/events","html_url":"https://github.com/modxcms/revolution/issues/15089","id":633550818,"node_id":"MDU6SXNzdWU2MzM1NTA4MTg=","number":15089,"title":"Wrong headline on edit content type modal dialog.","user":{"login":"pepebe","id":667315,"node_id":"MDQ6VXNlcjY2NzMxNQ==","avatar_url":"https://avatars3.githubusercontent.com/u/667315?v=4","gravatar_id":"","url":"https://api.github.com/users/pepebe","html_url":"https://github.com/pepebe","followers_url":"https://api.github.com/users/pepebe/followers","following_url":"https://api.github.com/users/pepebe/following{/other_user}","gists_url":"https://api.github.com/users/pepebe/gists{/gist_id}","starred_url":"https://api.github.com/users/pepebe/starred{